{"tid":2053870,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"斷言罷韓不會過，美麗島電子報董事長吳子嘉爆內幕","createTime":"2020-06-06T16:05:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-06T19:11:59.000Z","uid":52658,"like":15,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"851b4c966e494bf67fbc15998907291f9c826d4e","tid":2053870,"uid":52658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T16:05:40.000Z","msg":"吳子嘉在政論節目《關鍵時刻》表示，「我不但是韓國瑜專家，我還是民進黨專家」，他大膽斷言，韓國瑜的罷免不會過關，更指「韓國瑜已經逃過這一劫」。<br />\n<br />\n吳子嘉認為，道理一點也不複雜，封關民調的結果與罷免門檻差不多，身為罷免票的主導者，一定希望開出如70萬、80萬票的票數，才能確保過關，如果以一個人的動員成本100元來計算，可能需要七、八千萬元，誰要出這個錢？他表示，民調中顯示，一定會投罷免票的族群只是民進黨在高雄的基本盤，與韓國瑜一點關係都沒有。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://newtalk.tw/news/view/2020-05-26/412008\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewtalk.tw%2Fnews%2Fview%2F2020-05-26%2F412008&d=bCxsXTpKmrqj5N4FYztdx5MONXnVHdpXbsFGehQCOpI%3D&h=a809e460\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://newtalk.tw/news/view/2020-05-26/412008</a>"},{"pid":"e55aa147ccd0ae672ef0f6b569032953144b73c3","tid":2053870,"uid":53524,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T16:07:06.000Z","msg":"同溫層效應"},{"pid":"f920ebd6cffa049495d60b83967e5b32e190c697","tid":2053870,"uid":118120,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T16:08:19.000Z","msg":"藍絲 / 親共 果D 通常都係咁口氣自大, 覺得有錢大撚曬<br />\n莫視社會既公義人權等等"},{"pid":"687c015697f1a04bde2891728eefef922acec18a","tid":2053870,"uid":103230,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T16:09:16.000Z","msg":"封關民調的結果與罷免門檻差不多<br />\n<br />\n做乜鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9a1e1308a43638a6efb50fb9944ba34843a7d27","tid":2053870,"uid":52658,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"e55aa147ccd0ae672ef0f6b569032953144b73c3","tid":2053870,"uid":53524,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T16:07:06.000Z","msg":"同溫層效應"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T16:09:29.000Z","m